ir filter on 2019, 2020, 2021, 2022, and 2023 Ram 1500 truck models. We also discuss the basic function of the air filter for the engine and Blauparts' recommended Ram 1500 air filter change interval.\nRAM HOW TO\nHow To Reset Ram Oil Change Life Reminder Light (2019-2022 5th Gen)\nHuri Blau - November 24, 2022\nAfter completing a Ram oil change, many wonder how to turn the oil light on the dash off. It is relatively easy to reset the Ram oil change reminder light, also known as the oil life indicator. This helpful blog post and video outline how to reset the oil change interval reminder light on 2019 and newer 5th gen Ram 1500, 2500, 3500, and 4500 models.\nRAM TECH TIPS\nWhat Type of Transfer Case Fluid Does My Ram 1500 Take?\nHuri Blau - November 16, 2022\nWhen shopping for Ram 1500 transfer case fluid, many owners wonder what type of transfer case fluid their specific Ram model uses. Blauparts is here to help! In this blog article, we explain transfer case fluid specifications used in 2011-2022 Ram 1500. We also touch on the transfer case fluid types used in the older 2002-2010 Dodge Ram 1500 models. This post will help you determine the correct Ram 1500 transfer case fluid, part numbers, and fill capacities needed when changing your Ram 1500 transfer case fluid.\nView All Blog Posts\nWhat Our Customers Are Saying\nPrevious\nPorsche Cayenne Motor Oil Change Kit - 2013-16 - 3.0L Diesel - 5w30 Fully Synthetic USVO\nJaguar F-Type Motor Oil Change Kit - 2016-20 - 5.0L - 0w20 - AWD\nRating\nPrice\nQuality\nReview by RRSTL\nI purchased the kit for 50% of the price of the oil alone at the dealership...\nSee all reviews\nDec 4, 2022\nRavenol Gear Oil EPX 80W-90 GL-5 1L\nRating\nPrice\nQuality\nReview by Lexo\nSecond bottle of this stuff and my AWD Lexus is running better than ever.\nSee all reviews\nDec 2, 2022\nRavenol Gear Oil MTF-1 75W-85 GL-4 GL-5 1L\nRating\nPrice\nQuality\nReview by Lexo\nBottle of this stuff and my AWD Lexus is running better than ever.\nSee all 